WEBVTT

00:01.440 --> 00:02.400
A few days later

00:02.440 --> 00:04.400
The Son of Heaven's edict arrives

00:04.720 --> 00:06.480
While pardoning you

00:06.600 --> 00:08.560
Orders the traitor Chu Huan

00:08.560 --> 00:10.160
To be executed according to law

00:11.040 --> 00:11.880
That same year

00:11.880 --> 00:13.080
Prince of Ning Sikong Zheng

00:13.160 --> 00:14.680
Is enfeoffed as Crown Prince

00:15.160 --> 00:16.320
Chancellor Chen Dao

00:16.440 --> 00:18.400
Also serves as Eastern Palace Grand Tutor

00:19.880 --> 00:21.200
The surge of succession struggle

00:21.200 --> 00:22.800
Seems to have calmed

00:23.480 --> 00:25.760
Under Prince of Ning's strict guard

00:26.240 --> 00:28.200
You can only in remote lands

00:28.360 --> 00:30.800
Watch from afar the calm waters

00:31.160 --> 00:35.040
As a carefree prince fishing and playing with dogs

00:48.880 --> 00:50.480
Wei Kingdom unifies the north in one move

00:50.720 --> 00:51.680
And marches south

00:52.480 --> 00:53.440
I heard

00:53.800 --> 00:55.280
The order calling you to aid

00:55.280 --> 00:56.680
Is already on its way

01:09.400 --> 01:10.840
I know you want to return

01:16.000 --> 01:16.560
These years

01:16.560 --> 01:17.960
You've worked hard to build the border army

01:18.280 --> 01:20.440
And there are still some in court who favor you

01:20.720 --> 01:21.880
But once you show yourself

01:22.040 --> 01:23.600
If you lose, you'll be crushed to pieces

01:25.480 --> 01:27.400
What will happen to me and the child then?
